&lt;p&gt;Are you struck by a new thought? I was. You never think of tuscany as a place to hike. Every picture you see on the internet or in the movies is of rolling hills full of private vineyards and Tuscan farm houses, but Tuscany has tons of forest. &lt;/p&gt;
